NAME		valemail
SYNTAX		valemail <user>
		valemail -p
		valemail -d <user>
DESCRIPTION	Toggles the validation of a user's email address.
		If a user has a validated email address, they can use the
		M command in the mailer, will probably have further uses in
		the future.
		If auto-valemail is enabled, then the -p option will list
		all pending requests and the -d option can be used to cancel
		a request.
